# Belt-and-suspenders: any *.log file anywhere in the tree.  Runtime logs live
# under bin/ (already ignored) and tools/ has its own ignore rules, but any
# accidental escape (e.g. a developer dropping a .log next to a .csproj while
# diagnosing) won't get committed.
*.log

# UiaDump diagnostic logs (may contain message content)
tools/UiaDump/*.log

# RegionDump outputs — may contain WhatsApp message content; never commit
region-dump-*.png

# Superpowers planning docs (specs, plans) — local workflow only
docs/superpowers/